name: The Path
description:
It's drizzling and little foggy.
I badly needed a hike , just want to walk or run. Free from the idleness of my home.
I met a stranger along the path who is standing idle ,we had a chat and i moved on , the walk getting longer and longer, i was getting farther and farther away from my home , surprisingly i liked it. Don't know how long i walked ,my legs started paining and suddenly i want to go home. MY HOME. I started running towards it , I'm panting but I'm not stopping anytime soon. I will only rest once i get there. I'm running even harder and started feeling I'm not gonna make it.
My vision became blurry, and someone hit me in the head.
Then I realised I fell from the bed and it's all a dream ,felt great ful for staying inside my home. 

Stay indoors - Stay safe
